      "raw_text": "The new time table wen. into\neffect On the Great Northern yes\nterday. The eastbound Oriental\nLimited will arrive in Spokane at\n9:40 p. m. instead of at 9:15 a. m.\n1t Will leave at 9:55 p. m. The\nwestbound Oriental Limited will ar\nrive at GAS a. m. and will leave\nat z a. m. No. 4, eastbound, will\narrive at OILS a. m. and will de-\npart at $50 a. m. No. 8, west\nbound, will arrive at $40 p. m. and\nwill depart at 6 p. m.\n\n\nA feature of the new time card\nIs the addition of another passen-\nger train on the S. F. & N. This\ntrain will leave Spokane at 4:25\np. m. and will arrive at Spokane in\nthe morning at $50 This is ex-\npected to boom the summer bust\nness at Loon lake."
